dy-gaga-and-bruno-mars-to-perform-tribute-to-los-angeles-at-2025-grammys-3833739">Lady Gaga和Bruno Mars在2025年Grammys向洛杉矶致敬，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lady-Gaga-and-Bruno-Mars.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-and-John-Esparza-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lady-Gaga-and-Bruno-Mars.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-and-John-Esparza-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lady-Gaga-and-Bruno-Mars.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-and-John-Esparza-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lady-Gaga-and-Bruno-Mars.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-and-John-Esparza-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lady-Gaga-and-Bruno-Mars.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-and-John-Esparza-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lady-Gaga-and-Bruno-Mars.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-and-John-Esparza-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lady-Gaga-and-Bruno-Mars.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-and-John-Esparza-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruno-mars">Bruno Mars</a>将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">第67届格莱美奖</a>上向洛杉矶致敬。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522"><b>“ Joker：FolieàDeux”评论：Lady Gaga在挑衅性的监狱音乐剧中闪耀</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>2025年的仪式于明天晚上（2月2日）举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> ， <a href="https://nme-next.netlify.app/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> ， <a href="https://nme-next.netlify.app/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a> ， <a href="https://nme-next.netlify.app/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">Raye</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">Chris Martin</a>此前曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-chris-martin-st-vincent-stevie-wonder-lainey-wilson-herbie-hancock-and-more-join-performers-3833020">宣布为表演者</a>。</p><p>唱片学院的首席执行官小哈维·梅森（Harvey Mason Jr.）在一月份确认， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-2025-grammys-will-proceed-as-planned-confirms-recording-academy-ceo-3828582">尽管遭受了毁灭袭击洛杉矶今年早些时候的破坏，但仪式仍将按计划举行</a>，但会倍增筹款活动。</p><p>唱片学院和音乐界已经<a href="https://www.recordingacademy.com/news/la-fire-relief-musicares-recording-academy">发起了洛杉矶的消防努力</a>，并捐赠了100万美元，“为音乐界的个人和家庭提供立即的救济和长期支持，面临灾难导致的流离失所和损失。”</p><p>现在，有人透露，Gaga和Mars <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">获得了年度最佳歌曲的提名，并</a>以“ Die With a With smile”的曲目为“ Die Die with a smile”，他们将登上舞台，表演“对这座城市的特别致敬洛杉矶和受野火影响的人”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFgtS8qJ00J/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div st